<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, user-scalable=yes">
  <title>글쓰기 포털</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
</head>
<body class="center-page">
  <div class="portal-card">
    <h1 class="portal-title">글쓰기</h1>

    <form method="POST" action="/login" class="portal-form">
      <input name="name" placeholder="이름" required>
      <input name="id" placeholder="학번" required>
      <button type="submit" class="soft-btn">입장</button>
    </form>

    <div class="notice-card">
      <h3>권장 환경 안내</h3>
      <p>• 크롬(Chrome) 브라우저 사용을 권장합니다.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>